{"tid":804933,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"2012年TWINS廣東話大碟《2 BE FREE》","createTime":"2018-09-03T11:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T07:06:59.000Z","uid":118379,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d57af904c88ed83b09f693372fcc0c9fa56268f0","tid":804933,"uid":118379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"TrackList：<br />\n<br />\nCD<br />\n1)花生騷<br />\n2)大過天<br />\n3)交叉感染<br />\n4)上陣<br />\n5)旅遊書<br />\n6) 金不換<br />\n7) 綁架<br />\n8) Let Me Fly Away<br />\n9) 素顏<br />\n10) 本小姐<br />\n<br />\n點解我一首歌都冇聽過？<br />\n<br />\n一首都冇<br />\n<br />\n我2012年向香港架喎 睇左對上一次Twins演唱會 <br />\n一首都冇聽過佢地唱<br />\n<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a57fe79caa33cce95f76310de329da7b10e7f92","tid":804933,"uid":85774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"因為垃圾"},{"pid":"38ed8bc6d524944661140ff05ce4404546720f1e","tid":804933,"uid":118379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"Twins隻隻碟都咁多宣傳<br />\n<br />\n點解呢隻碟可以隱形到咁？"},{"pid":"0d574508b5b7ba168f4d83c9040619340c16937b","tid":804933,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:01:37.000Z","msg":"真係有出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全無聽過"},{"pid":"842ff94790fc19d3ea62a6256acc09b2791350c3","tid":804933,"uid":4217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"大過天有聽過"},{"pid":"9a58fa3d9b3e74b2013401e477f33676224d1556","tid":804933,"uid":14036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"淨係聽過大過天同綁架<br />\n講緊歌名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻碟演唱會冇唱過都冇人投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f4940a9288662455170155e1ddd3094dc5